-- U.S. Asks Courts to Dismiss Oil Industry Challenge to Deep-Water Drill Ban
-- Laurel Brubaker Calkins
-- 2010-07-12T23:41:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/u-s-asks-courts-to-dismiss-oil-industry-challenge-to-deep-water-drill-ban.html

          
          
             Interior Secretary Kenneth
Salazar asked two New Orleans courts to dismiss an industry
lawsuit challenging a U.S. deep-water drilling moratorium,
saying a new drill ban made the suit irrelevant.  
